nodes.metaTitle: Crypto Wallet: Manage BTC, ETH & LTC with our app

content.title: The simplest all-in-one mobile crypto wallet

childMarkdownRemark.html:
• Buy bitcoin with a few taps in the app
  • Receive instantly, safely secured in your wallet
  • Purchase bitcoin using credit card or SOFORT

• Exchange BTC to ETH and vice versa
  • Seamless and instant crypto exchange
  • Transparent fees and a fuss-free experience

• Store, send, and receive bitcoin, ether, litecoin, and PAY Token
  • Advanced security and multi-sig storage safeguards your crypto

• Monitor market prices right from TenX app
  • Price alerts to help you make smarter buying decisions

• Advanced control settings for your TenX Visa Card
  • Instantly disable/enable online, contactless, swipe, or chip payments
  • 2-Factor Authentication for added security

• Track complete incoming and outgoing wallet transactions
  • See detailed card transaction history and monthly overviews

faqs.question: Is your crypto wallet free to use?

childMarkdownRemark.html: Yes, you can use the TenX Wallet to store, send, and receive crypto for free. Supported cryptocurrencies: bitcoin, ether, litecoin, and the PAY Token.

faqs.question: How do I sign up for a crypto account?

childMarkdownRemark.html: Simply download the TenX app and go through the onboarding process, and you’re set!
Absolutely, security is our top priority. Along with our E-Money License granted by the FMA of Liechtenstein, we bring you a suite of security measures to ensure your funds are always protected.
